# Legal Pages Conventions

Load `.cursor/skills/legal-pages/SKILL.md` when editing matched files.

## Layout

- Use `LegalPage` from `src/components/LegalPage.tsx` for all legal routes
- Content lives in `src/content/*.ts` as `LegalDocument` exports
- Body text: `text-[15px] text-white/70 leading-relaxed` inside `liquid-glass-strong` panel
- Include `lastUpdated` in header; bump on material policy changes

